query:
SELECT n.id, n.customerId, n.type, n.title, n.message, n.createdAt, c.email, c.pin 
FROM notifications n 
LEFT JOIN customers c ON n.customerId = c.id 
WHERE c.email = 'fcokelrihbrito@gmail.com' 
ORDER BY n.createdAt DESC 
LIMIT 5
